def count_time(func, *data):
    tick = time.perf_counter()
    func(*data)
    return time.perf_counter() - tick

def pplot(n, not_v_t, v_t, title):
  fig, ax = plt.subplots()
  plt.xlabel("   ")
  plt.ylabel(" (c)")
  fig.set_figwidth(10)
  fig.set_figheight(5)
  plt.xscale('log')
  plt.title(title)
  ax.plot(n, not_v_t, label = u' ')
  ax.plot(n, v_t, label = u' ')
  plt.legend()
  plt.grid(True)
  plt.show()
